public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        try {
            int a = 10 / 2;
            System.out.println("Result: " + a);

        } catch (Exception e) {
            System.out.println("Error occurred");

        } finally {
            // always executes
            System.out.println("Execution completed");
        }
    }
}
Interview Explanation

finally always runs

Used for cleanup (DB close, file close)
